## 2. Services

The Artist will provide the services described in the booking details and any attached quote, invoice, package description or written scope agreed by the Parties.

Unless otherwise agreed in writing, the services include:

1. attendance at the event for the agreed service period;
2. live watercolour painting in the Artist’s distinctive style;
3. the number, size and type of artwork/s stated in the booking details;
4. reasonable preparation before the event, including review of information provided by the Client;
5. reasonable post-event finishing or touch-ups where included in the selected package; and
6. delivery or handover of the completed artwork as described in this Agreement.

The Artist is engaged as an independent creative professional and is not an employee, agent or servant of the Client.

